                shrine of Sikhism. It symbolizes human equality and brotherhood</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 2 -->
        <div class="card">
            <h3>Uttrakhand</h3>
            <img src="pics/uttrakhand.jpg" alt="Image 2">
            <p>Uttarakhand:also known as ‘Devbhumi’ or ‘Land of Gods’, is a northern Indian state nestled between the
                Tibetan Plateau and the Indo-Gangetic Plains</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 3 -->
        <div class="card">
               <h3>Rajasthan</h3>
            <img src="pics/rajasthan.jpg" alt="Image 3">
            <p>Rajasthan:Kumbhalgarh, a UNESCO World Heritage Site, is a majestic fortress located in Rajasthan, India1.
                Known as the “Great Wall of India”, it boasts the world’s second-longest continuous wall</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer>
        <h2>
            Subscribe & <br> get special discount
        </h2><br>
        <p>Travel: the only thing you buy that makes you richer. Explore, dream, discover!</p>
        <br>
        <div class="input">
            <input type="text" placeholder="Enter your Email Address">
            <button> Subscribe</button>
        </div>
        <ul>
            <li> 7865 <br>
                <h6>Year Serving The Travel Industry</h6>
            </li>
            <li> 4567 <br>
                <h6> Global <br> Paternship</h6>
            </li>
            <li> 7844 <br>
                <h6> Industry Award Since 2022 </h6>
            </li>
            <li> 6000 <br>
                <h6> Subscribe</h6>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </footer>

    <!-- Bootstrap Icons CDN -->
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/js/brands.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/js/solid.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/js/fontawesome.js"></script>
</body>

</html>